To compile please make sure you have installed:
blas
lapack
fftw3
all of them freely accessible and available in the installers of
many Linux distros.

After having the above library simplity type
make
in the directory holding the present file.

To run you need three files in the running directory:
Gamma.dat  that includes two broadenings
Hamiltonian.dat that includes the electronic level
WNnca.input that has all the parameters of the run including the vibrational modes and coupligns

You can download the present code from git https://github.com/qphensurf/NEncaVIB

Nicolas Lorente

